# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Folio — Client Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The frontend currently uses relative API paths (/api/...) and relies on
# the Express backend to serve it in production (no VITE_ vars are required
# for the standard Render monorepo deployment).
#
# If you deploy the frontend separately on Vercel, you would add:
#
#   VITE_API_URL=https://<your-backend>.onrender.com
#
# and update all fetch() calls to use import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL as prefix.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
